<div class="com-share" data-id="23950" data-title="《索尼的虚拟现实头盔开始预订， 450 美元其实没那么便宜｜GDC》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23950/medium/23950.jpg?1458098059" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23950.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
